A Long Time Ago.

25
00:03:08,710 --> 00:03:10,190
Very quietly, I take my leave.

26
00:03:11,910 --> 00:03:13,840
As quietly as I came here.

27
00:03:13,910 --> 00:03:15,520
Some numbers change while some don't.

28
00:03:15,680 --> 00:03:17,030
