32
00:03:22,430 --> 00:03:23,840
Homie!

33
00:03:28,520 --> 00:03:30,280
Leave, Your Grace!

34
00:03:30,910 --> 00:03:31,750
Go!

35
00:03:41,310 --> 00:03:42,400
- Shaoheng.
- Your Highness.

36
00:03:42,480 --> 00:03:44,160
- Someone wants to kill you.
- Someone wants to burn you.

37
00:03:51,190 --> 00:03:53,000
Buddy, could I talk to you?

38
00:03:54,960 --> 00:03:56,000
Cheers.

39
00:03:58,520 --> 00:04:00,150
Life here is really painful.

40
00:04:00,430 --> 00:04:02,560
I can't eat regularly or sleep well.

41
00:04:02,910 --> 00:04:05,000
Every day, I do hard work as a maid.

42
00:04:05,020 --> 00:04:07,040
When I was drinking just now,
I didn't even dare to drink too much,

43
00:04:07,120 --> 00:04:08,520
in case this fierce prince

44
00:04:08,520 --> 00:04:09,590
killed me by accident.

45
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:11,030
If I knew you were from my world,

46
00:04:11,190 --> 00:04:12,030
I wouldn't be scared.

47
00:04:12,150 --> 00:04:13,190
You're right.

48
00:04:13,400 --> 00:04:14,840
It's hard to be this fierce prince, too.

49
00:04:15,240 --> 00:04:16,270
Within only a few days,

50
00:04:16,480 --> 00:04:18,190
I've been assassinated five times.

51
00:04:20,240 --> 00:04:23,480
Yeah. Being a prince is quite risky.

52
00:04:24,600 --> 00:04:25,560
It is pretty strange.

53
00:04:26,270 --> 00:04:27,110
Think about it.

54
00:04:27,390 --> 00:04:29,120
Only a few of us knew this trip.

55
00:04:29,480 --> 00:04:30,320
How would the...

56
00:04:30,360 --> 00:04:31,920
Someone must have stalked us.

57
00:04:33,480 --> 00:04:35,270
Well, never mind. Let's drink.

58
00:04:35,270 --> 00:04:36,110
Cheers.

59
00:04:36,800 --> 00:04:37,750
Have you met Zhang San?

60
00:04:37,950 --> 00:04:38,790
Yes, of course.

61
00:04:38,950 --> 00:04:40,720
That terrible guy gave me a mission

62
00:04:40,720 --> 00:04:41,950
to bathe you.

63
00:04:44,750 --> 00:04:46,190
Come on. Let's drink.

64
00:04:52,360 --> 00:04:54,360
I haven't seen him
for a long time, though.

65
00:04:54,920 --> 00:04:57,000
We don't need to stay here forever,
do we?

66
00:04:57,250 --> 00:04:58,950
He said we could leave
after completing the mission.

67
00:04:59,870 --> 00:05:00,710
By the way,

68
00:05:00,950 --> 00:05:02,000
what is your mission?

69
00:05:02,390 --> 00:05:03,270
How's that going?

70
00:05:05,430 --> 00:05:06,270
Forget about that.

71
00:05:06,480 --> 00:05:07,600
Let's drink.

72
00:05:08,000 --> 00:05:08,840
Cheers.

73
00:05:11,920 --> 00:05:13,120
Is it done?

74
00:05:13,600 --> 00:05:14,440
Chief,

75
00:05:14,600 --> 00:05:15,720
Shen Juanjuan failed.

76
00:05:16,830 --> 00:05:17,720
Where's she?

77
00:05:18,270 --> 00:05:19,680
She went back with Prince Heng.

78
00:05:25,920 --> 00:05:28,070
Oh, Xingchen.

79
00:05:29,360 --> 00:05:30,800
I'll go get her back now.

80
00:05:34,830 --> 00:05:35,920
Losers.

81
00:05:36,800 --> 00:05:38,000
None of them can help at all.

82
00:05:39,950 --> 00:05:42,270
I want to go home.

83
00:05:43,120 --> 00:05:45,040
I miss my mother.

84
00:05:46,270 --> 00:05:50,800
Fried chicken, beer, barbecue,
Honor of Kings,

85
00:05:52,270 --> 00:05:53,360
and...

86
00:05:54,720 --> 00:05:57,240
I can't think of anything else.

87
00:06:03,630 --> 00:06:05,720
What else is there?

88
00:06:07,160 --> 00:06:08,000
Oh, no.

89
00:06:09,560 --> 00:06:10,510
I want to work.

90
00:06:11,600 --> 00:06:12,560
I want to have some meetings.

91
00:06:53,190 --> 00:06:54,120
Sorry.

92
00:06:54,120 --> 00:06:55,480
I was drunk last night.

93
00:06:55,480 --> 00:06:57,070
Pretend nothing happened.

94
00:06:57,750 --> 00:06:59,120
Nothing happened exactly.

95
00:07:06,190 --> 00:07:08,720
(Isn't it a great chance?)

96
00:07:11,120 --> 00:07:13,560
(Shen Juan, you have fallen.)

97
00:07:13,560 --> 00:07:14,920
(He's a human.)

98
00:07:15,040 --> 00:07:17,240
