just to get back home?)

99
00:07:19,560 --> 00:07:20,680
From this day on,

100
00:07:20,800 --> 00:07:22,390
I'll be your savior.

101
00:07:25,360 --> 00:07:26,510
Mr. Novel,

102
00:07:27,070 --> 00:07:28,480
